        "TileImage": "$($repository 872ef621-7fe3-4ab3-80d5-f689a5bbd950).Image",
        "Description": "You have been tasked with neutralizing a child sex trafficking ring in Bangkok, Thailand. Shielded by corrupt officials and the lax enforcement of laws, the ring has wreaked havoc on innocent lives across South Asia. With the support of his agent, Jordan Cross and his lawyer pursue their evil trade with impunity. Facilitated by its manager and security chief, the Himmapan Hotel serves as the base of the ring&apos;s operations. Deliver overdue justice to the five members of the ring.",
